description:
Coming April 4th

Since killing Apple Bottom's parents, Care Package has taken him into his home. When Apple Bottom expresses interest in joining one of Care Package's "hunts," the postal pony eagerly takes his cute little "pet" under his wing. But when Twilight Sparkle and friends find themselves to be the target of tonights hunt, all kinds of clownery ensues
